parameters:
Tailor Nil No matter how many times I'm asked, I won't
change. I am a true artist... I hope you understand, don't
you?
Clea: Is this person the tailor?

Thief Nora: Roses, lilies, love... They never listen to what
I have to say~

Mage Relm: I felt sick from the shaking of the box. Sigh, I
stopped drinking wine though.

Priestess Sophia: Nfuu, nhaa, haa haa... Ufufu, don't get so
angry, Lilum-chan.
Priestess Sophia: I-I'm coming over there right now~

Priestess Sophia: Sigh, I had a terrible experience. If only
they had carried it more carefully, this wouldn't have
happened--
Priestess Sophia: Who might this person be~?

Mage Relm: Normally, you would hit someone before asking...
Honestly.
Clea: I think I'll do the same.
Tailor Nil: I'll take the request! I'll make a dress!
Tailor Nil: Instead! Instead, have her wear my new creation!

Priestess Sophia: I'm not sure about the context of the
conversation, but if it's okay with me, I don't mind~

Tailor Nil: Come on, come on, come on, deeper! This is
amazing, ahahaha, it's the best day!

Priestess Sophia: It fits me so perfectly... It's as if it
was tailored just for me.

Tailor Nil: I was looking for a swimsuit, someone who would
make me shine even more! You are amazing, you are beautiful,
you are the best!
Priestess Sophia: I don't mind being praised that much.
Priestess Sophia: Hehe, I wonder how it is?
Thief Nora: It suits you so well!
Clea: Yes, it suits Sophia perfectly.
Mage Relm: You're suitable enough to compete against me!

Tailor Nil: This swimsuit was inspired by the recluse Hora,
who was known as the Thorn of the Black Rose. I would like
to present it to you as a tribute to your dangerous beauty.
Tailor Nil: Amazing, ah, what beauty... Next is you!
Thief Nora: Ah, is it me!?

Tailor Nil: Wild charm, it suits you, but I have an
imperfect swimsuit for you!

Tailor Nil: I have a request for you all! Please obtain a
red coral for this swimsuit!

Thief Nora: B-But I can't just accept a request without
permission...
Clea: Understood, I will accept the request.

Clea: Let's have swimsuits made so that everyone will have
one.
Thief Nora: Yes! Thank you very much!

Tailor Nil: I'll take on Cors' request as a way to pass the
time, looking forward to meeting you all again!
実績 海賊と売春島
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Tailor Nil The true red lies in the depths of the sea...
It's a dangerous request, but I'll do it for the sake of
perfect beauty!
Tailor Nil Now, let's create another work of art today!

Tailor Nil: Hey, welcome back! I've been experimenting and
I've created something interesting.

Tailor Nil: Would you guys be willing to wear it if you'd
like?
